1. Go to https://rlcard.org/ and install the rlcard
2. copy thegame folder to rlcard/games
3. copy envs folder to rlcard/envs
4. Currently the reward is: after take the action, if the next state has at least one legal action, the reward is 1; if the next state has no leagal action, the reward is -1. You can change the reward to try your idea.
5. Currently the game is a simpler version with 48 cards(2-50) which can run faster than the real game.
